principal.note:
Commissioned as Presidential Special Representative and Adviser on African, Asian,
                and Latin American Affairs. Commissioned during a recess of the Senate;
                recommissioned after confirmation on Jan 30, 1962.

Commissioned as U.S. Coordinator for Refugee Affairs and Ambassador at Large;
                designated Mar 5, 1987, to serve concurrently as Director of the Bureau of Refugee
                Programs
